\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... Nice, this looks like it's going to be quite
entertaining.
\N<Luda Soldier>Lord Zuuteruka, what are you looking at?
\N<Zuuteruka>Ah, this.

\N<Luda Soldier>The tournament bracket for the training soldiers? I see, so
this boy is the next opponent for that woman. He seems quite
young though...

\N<Zuuteruka>Hey, don't underestimate someone just because they're young.
This Fubii guy has proven his skills. He's rumored to have
destroyed a band of thieves in the past, you know?

\N<Luda Soldier>Destroyed a band of thieves? This boy did? That's a hard
story to believe...

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... Well, let's thoroughly witness this rumored
strength of his. Whatever the case, he's not an opponent to
be underestimated. Now, what will happen, I wonder?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hey, Segi. You're late.
\N<Segi>...What do you want?

\N<Zuuteruka>Don't glare at me like that. I just thought I should inform
you about your next opponent.
\N<Segi>...
\N<Zuuteruka>Here, this guy is your next match.
\N<Segi>He is...
\N<Zuuteruka>Huh? What? Do you know him?
\N<Segi>...It's none of your business.

\N<Zuuteruka>Oh, is that so? I was just about to tell you that you can't
let your guard down with this opponent.
\N<Segi>...

\N<Zuuteruka>You shouldn't be fooled by appearances, you know? After all,
despite his youth, he's notorious for having slaughtered a
whole band of thieves just to avenge his grudge.

\N<Segi>...Who he is doesn't matter. I will simply devote all my
efforts to what I must do.

\N<Zuuteruka>Ah, is that so? More importantly, have you made up your
mind? Huh?
\N<Segi>Made up my mind? What are you talking about?

\N<Zuuteruka>Heh, it's obvious, isn't it? You're preparing yourself to
become mine, body and soul, literally.

\N<Zuuteruka>Relax, I'm not saying I'll make you a slave. Instead of
Yuia, I'll take good care of you and cherish you. It's a
woman's ultimate joy, right?
\N<Segi>...You're quite the confident one.

\N<Zuuteruka>There's no reason for you to hesitate, right? It's all good
for you.

\N<Segi>Stop joking. What else could possibly exist between you and
me other than the worst thing?

\N<Zuuteruka>Heh... What are you even saying? You're practically half my
woman already.

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... Don't break your promise, okay? I'm looking
forward to three days from now. That's when it'll be crystal
clear who you belong to.
\N<Segi>Grr...!

\N<Luda Soldier>Excuse me. The woman in question has arrived. She requests
an audience with Lord Zuuteruka.
\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... So she's come. Let her in, will you?
\N<Zuuteruka>You've done well. You may stand down.
\N<Luda Soldier>Yes...
\N<Segi>...
\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... So you've come, Segi.

\N<Segi>Let me make this clear from the start... I'm not here to
engage in idle chatter with you, nor to rekindle old ties.

\N<Segi>I've merely come to fulfill your vile desires. I'm here to
bestow mercy upon you, pitiful as you are.

\N<Segi>And as a result... I expect you to keep your promise to
allow me to rejoin the training corps. That's the sole
reason I'm here.

\N<Segi>I have no intention of wasting time. So spare me any
unnecessary talk.

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, quite the attitude for someone in a position to beg.
But that's part of your charm, isn't it?
\N<Segi>...

\N<Zuuteruka>Well, fine. If that's what you wish, let's get straight to
the point.
\N<Segi>...Please do.

\N<Zuuteruka>Your husband is chained in prison. And for a crime so grave
that it warrants the death penalty.

\N<Segi>Don't make me repeat myself. There is no crime to speak of
when it comes to Lord Yuia... my husband. If there is, it's
nothing but a fabrication by you Ludas.

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, don't play dumb. That might work on the others, but
it won't fly with me.
\N<Segi>...

\N<Zuuteruka>And for the sake of saving that husband of yours, you agreed
to the terms of the training corps and took to the stage in
accordance with Luda's rules.

\N<Zuuteruka>If you go back on that, Yuia himself will face a hanging
after a trial in absentia. And who knows what might happen
to you.
\N<Segi>...

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... And let's not forget about your cute little son.
Even an innocent young boy with a future ahead of him might
be implicated, right?

\N<Segi>...You will not lay a hand on Riia. If you dare to do such a
thing, I will kill you right here and now.

\N<Segi>Understand? This is not a threat. I came here prepared for
just that.
\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, I understand, this is just a confirmation.
\N<Segi>What... do you want me to do?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... You catch on quick. It's good to have a woman who
learns fast.

\N<Zuuteruka>Tonight, you become mine. In exchange for rejoining the
training corps, you will become my woman.

\N<Zuuteruka>From tonight on, you're no longer Yuia's wife. You'll be my
mistress. You came here tonight prepared for that, didn't
you?
\N<Segi>...
\N<Segi>Don't make me say it again...

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, I like that look in your eyes. It sends shivers down
my spine. Alright, if that's settled, come over here. My new
mistress deserves a grand unveiling before my men, doesn't
she?
\N<Segi>...
\N<Segi>...

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, don't make such a face. Well, rest assured. As long
as you keep your part of that particular promise, I don't
care how many times you're defeated.

\N<Zuuteruka>No matter how many times you taste defeat, you won't be
excluded from the training soldiers' assembly. As long as
your reason and spirit hold out... right?
\N<Segi>...

\N<Zuuteruka>So remember... don't forget, okay? You must fulfill your
duties as my mistress.

\N<Zuuteruka>Got it? It's the night before the next match. You must come
here on that evening without fail.

\N<Zuuteruka>If you keep to that and remain obedient, only then will you
be allowed to continue fighting in the training soldiers'
assembly. That's what keeps Yuia's life hanging by a thread.
\N<Segi>...
\N<Segi>...Let me see Lord Yuia.

\N<Zuuteruka>Oh? What's this? Planning to bid farewell to your beloved
husband? "I will belong to this man~. So, it's goodbye to
you~" or something like that?

\N<Segi>Haven't I told you not to wag your useless tongue? Just
hurry up and show me the way...
\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... Alright, alright, such a demanding woman.
C
